{{Quote|Ros Lai! Come and imbibe some warm yeade with your sisters!|[[Vonya]] to [[Ros Lai]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1998) 23">[[Star Wars (1998) 23|''Star Wars'' (1998) 23]]</ref>}}
'''Yeade''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] drink enjoyed by the [[Witches of Dathomir]]. It was usually served warm and particularly appreciated during cold weather. The Sisters who guarded the [[maleling]]s at night would often get drunk on yeade.

In [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]], the [[Witch/Legends|witch]] [[Vonya]] once bullied her fellow Sister [[Ros Lai]] by [[Telekinesis/Legends|throwing]] a cauldron of hot yeade at her face.

